put for `0.3.1`.\n\nManual next steps:\n- Review the preserved test change on the branch and rerun `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.lihaoyi:sourcecode_3:0.3.1` to confirm the JVM fix is the right behavioral update.\n- Fix the GraalVM / `native-image-agent` environment and rerun metadata generation or native verification for `com.lihaoyi:sourcecode_3:0.3.1`.\n- Regenerate stats for `0.3.1` after metadata generation succeeds, and confirm `metadata/com.lihaoyi/sourcecode_3/0.3.1` plus final coverage output are produced."}}
